{"tid":698114,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【北角新盤】柏蔚山次輪收逾1400票 超額約3.6倍","createTime":"2018-06-11T12:03:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-11T14:06:16.000Z","uid":68476,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"731f1223bcb9e81c0561ec5e07f102f2ab1b7f54","tid":698114,"uid":68476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T12:03:11.000Z","msg":"【北角新盤】柏蔚山次輪收逾1400票 超額約3.6倍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180611/large/1528713641_a5b0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180611%2Flarge%2F1528713641_a5b0.jpg&h=76a8e5a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新世界（017）北角柏蔚山今午12時截票，消息指項目收逾1400票，超額認購約3.6倍。項目明早於荃灣愉景新城售樓處開售次輪300伙，訂價市值逾88億元，當中涉68伙一房戶、78伙兩房戶、120伙三房戶及34伙四房戶。次輪入場單位為3座6樓C室一房戶，實用面積519方呎，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>折實價1383.1萬元，呎價26,649元。</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41126fc2d731f6c7bd5e2366ff5e508863aaecc1","tid":698114,"uid":90601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T14:06:16.000Z","msg":"依家連恆基樓都可以即日沽清 已經唔知可以用咩去形容樓市 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}